==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: pervaporation
<hw>pervaporation</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The concentration of a
colloidal solution whose colloid will not pass through a semipermeable
membrane; the solution is placed in a bag of the membrane and the
solvent is evaporated off.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pervasion</ent>⟦br⟧
